@1000 = ~Oooh, the master has a tongue-blade from Avernus!~
@1001 = ~I can makes the tongue-blade even better with a silver Gith-hilt to reforge.~
@1002 = ~Let me sees if the master has what I need to reforge the tongue-blade...~
@1003 = ~I thoughts maybe you have pieces for Heartwood Ring. Good recipe for druid. But you needs both oaken ring and a nymph's tear. That a gem, if you not know. But who cares?  Or....yes, can also use elemental stone, that's a gem too, just saying...~
@1004 = ~You would like Cespenar to improve the blaze-tongue-blade for the master?~
@1005 = ~Cespenar would need somethings special, like an Eye of Ichor to make blade better.~
@1006 = ~Ooh, and you gots the Eye of Ichor. 15,000 gp and I will makes the master a most hellish tongue-blade indeed, hehe.~
@1007 = ~I is so excited the master is using one of our very own blades, Let's sees what else you has.~
@1008 = ~Hmm, soft bootses for feet?~
@1009 = ~I can makes softboots better with some liquid mercury.~
