@2000 = ~Long Sword~
@2001 = ~Tongue of Acid +3~
@2002 = ~This infernal longsword, forged to resemble a devil's tongue, has a blade "sharper than any scream" according to the writing on the hilt. Its edge cuts easily through armor and bone and leaves acid sizzling in the wounds it inflicts. The pain its wounds inflict is so severe that its victims have difficulty functioning, even walking, due to the agony.

STATISTICS:

