– Lore: -60
– Constitution: +1
– Intelligence: +1
– Armor Class: +1
– Save vs. Death: +4
– Magic Resistance: 5%

Weight: 1~
@2022 = ~Horned Helm of Dumathoin~
@2023 = ~With the horns added, the helm of Dumathoin can deflect even the fiercest blows from any physical attack, and improves the constitution of the wearer.  The glory of Dumathoin really shines in this helmet.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
– Armor Class +1
