Weight: 1~
@2024 = ~Archer's Eagle Eyes~
@2025 = ~The pair of eyes that form the charm of this amulet have taken on a clear, crystalline glow, almost alive in appearance, and now impart even greater skill to archers.  In addition, the wearer may conjure a wizard eye for scouting twice per day.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
