Charge abilities:
– Wizard Eye twice per day
  Special: Creates an invisible eye that can see with normal vision in brightly lit areas, user is subject to gaze attacks
  Range: 60 ft.

Weight: 1~
@2026 = ~Belt of the Blademaster~
@2027 = ~Say'an Keenedge would be pleased to see any of her blades in the hands of the wearer of this belt.  With the additional enchantments placed on the belt, even the most novice swordsman can swing a blade with skill and accuracy.

STATISTICS:

