@2030 = ~Vampiric Voidsword +5~
@2031 = ~By absorbing the dark magics contained in the lich's skull, the Voidsword's hunger has been amplified greatly.  Strikes from the blade now do more damage, and there is a chance on hit of draining strength and life from all enemies within a 15' radius.  The life drained from the targets is transferred to the weilder, healing <PRO_HESHE> for the amount of damage done.  Undead, however are still unaffected by this weapon or its effects.

