@2034 = ~Hat~
@2035 = ~Melodious Bard Hat~
@2036 = ~With the additional magical enchantments endowed upon the bard hat, the precocious wearer is now better protected in addition to their vocal improvements and also increases their intelligence, making this hat a far more practical choice for the travelling troubador.

