Weight: 4~
@2039 = ~Mirrored Buckler of the Fist +2~
@2040 = ~This flame-emblazoned buckler has been expertly recrafted, imparting magics from a dormant former festhall decoration collecting dust in an Amnish shop.  The shield now has reflective properties and can send missile barrages back to the wearer's assailants.

