@2041 = ~Sundermaul +3~
@2042 = ~Legends speak of a hammer with the power of the gods themselves called Crom Faeyr. A smith once forged an inferior hammer and claimed it Crom Faeyr. Such was the retribution of the gods that ever since, when the name "Crom Faeyr" is uttered, the very earth beneath the weilder's feet may rip and tear asunder, threatening to bury the blasphemer and any who happen to be standing nearby.

