@2045 = ~The Scorched Earth +3~
@2046 = ~Expertly reforged for <CHARNAME>, the flame tongue is now a far more balanced blade and searing flames scorch enemies with every slash, leaving charred wounds in its wake.  The sword remains very effective against cold-based, regenerating creatures, and the undead.

STATISTICS:

Combat abilities:
