@2047 = ~Star-Strewn Boots~
@2048 = ~These boots belonged to Crommus the Minstrel many centuries ago. When Artipheon the mage slew Crommus and severed the bard's voice, some of Artipheon's power infused Crommus's boots. The once ordinary midnight-blue leather boots now glitter as if hundreds of twinkling stars were embedded in the material.

STATISTICS:

Equipped abilities:
– Magic Resistance: +7%, +15% (Wizard Slayers)

Weight: 4~
@2049 = ~Star-Strewn Boots of Antimagic~
@2050 = ~Crommus' boots have been meticulously re-cobbled for <CHARNAME>, further improving their ability to shield their wearer from magical attacks.  The boots now also have a limited ability to envelop the wearer in a protective shell of antimagic, preventing all magic from affecting the wearer for a short duration.  

