@2562 = ~Scimitar~
@2563 = ~The Lucky Scimitar +3~
@2564 = ~The scimitar is closely related to the saber, a single-edged curved sword with protective hilt. The blade has a greater curve to it and is tapered to an elongated, sharp point. The origins of the scimitar are largely unknown; however, they have been very popular in the southern region of the realms.

