@2592 = ~Kontik, a powerful wizard in the service of Auril, claimed this ring from a defeated enemy wizard, Nill the Infernal. An archmage who specialized in fire magic, Nill created the ring over a period of five years. The powerful item aided Nill in his far-ranging travels. Unfortunately for Nill, it did not protect him from Kontik's powerful minions and spells. It is constructed of an extremely unusual grayish-white metal called tungsten.

