@2597 = ~Edion's Ring of Wizardry~
@2598 = ~Edion, a dying necromancer from Sembia, was the recent owner of this powerful ring. He crafted the ring himself for his private use. In his later years, he became so accustomed to wearing it that he almost never removed it. He wore it on the same finger that he would wear a wedding ring on, to symbolize his marriage to the Art.

